testcase.title: Export Search Service for Site dataset verifying the coulumn name country being changed to Country/Territory

steps.title: I am authenticated user accessing "SOAP" API

I pass a "applicationId = ngapi#1756 and userId = API and dataSet = site and searchQuery = cancer and queryLanguage = ssql and returnFields = siteCountry and returnLimit = 10 and offset = 0 and expectedValues = sitefile_001.xls and exportFormat = MS-EXCEL and wrapText = True" as parameter to "exportsearchservice" operation
check the requested file is found in the following path "sitefile_001.xls"
check for all the columns "Country/Territory" in the file
